H3.text: In which town did the Co-operative Movement begin. ROCHDALE

A4.text: The Rochdale Society of Equitable Pioneers was founded in Rochdale in 1844.

A5.text: The Rochdale Pioneers co-operative became the prototype for societies in Great Britain.
